 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Immunity:

    This Pokémon cannot be poisoned. 
  This includes bad poison.

  If a Pokémon is poisoned and 
  acquires this ability, its poison 
  is healed; this includes when 
  regaining a lost ability upon 
  leaving battle.

  Thick-fat:

    This Pokémon takes half as 
  much damage from fire- and ice-type 
  moves.

  Gluttony:

    This Pokémon eats any held 
  Berry triggered by low HP when 
  it falls below 50% of its HP, 
  regardless of the Berry's usual 
  threshold.


 Location Areas:
   Kanto route 12 area
   Vermilion city area
   Kanto route 11 area
   Kanto route 16 area
